# Generated by build.rs when the `mcp_local_dev` Cargo feature is on.
# See build.rs and CLAUDE.md / agent.md "Local Tauri MCP Bridge".
/capabilities/mcp-bridge.json

# Tauri-generated capability / permission schemas. Regenerated on every
# GUI build and they absorb the dev-only `mcp-bridge` capability when the
# `mcp_local_dev` feature is on, which produces constant churn. Treat them
# as build artifacts — the build recreates them from the capability files.
/gen/schemas/
